lender.name: Fairific
lender.loan_because: The best way to find yourself is to lose yourself in the service of others – Mahatma Gandhi
lender.occupational_info:
Our mission is simple: to bring you quality, useful, affordable stuff from ethical sources everywhere and make it Fairific for All.
Fairific for All means that artisans and craftspeople get treated fairly as business partners so that they can make the things our stylish, socially conscious community wants. As part of the Fairific community, you’re smart, high energy gals and guys, and even so we know that the mix of alternative, ethical, fair, and direct trade can be confusing. This is our take: basically, it’s a question of helping people talk to each other and closing the loop. We help you talk to the folks who make Fairific stuff about what you like so they can make it and become better competitors in the marketplace. Life is better for everyone when you get what you want and they get honest help. To us, that human connection is the backbone of ethical trade.
In ethical trade, we create opportunity for the folks who make our stuff by ending their isolation and treating them the same way you and the rest of our Fairific community want to be treated. It seems to us that people want to lead safe, comfortable, and purposeful lives with a sense of opportunity for themselves, their communities, and their children. They want to be themselves, do good work that improves rather than damages the natural world, and be compensated fairly so that their kids can imagine, explore, and enjoy a great future. That’s our basic set of social and environmental values.
Fair Trade and other third party certifications help us make sure that our values are upheld, and so do your personal ethical standards. We give you a big ol’ seal of approval to use on the products that you vote good enough, making you and the community a legit ethical trade certifier. To help you speak your mind and find what you’re looking for, we’ve built the Fair-o-Sphere, made up of our website, mobile app, and a network of in-store selling systems in brick-and-mortar stores right here in the U.S. of A.
The website, Fairific.com, is our home base, and it ties the whole Fairific experience together. It’s a place where everyone from go-getters to slacktivists and fair minds of all stripes can come together to shop, share, and noodle around in the
community space. In it you’ll find stuff like the Voting System, a mechanism that lets you decide what’s swell enough and fair enough to be part of Fairific. Our Blog is where we keep track of all the yummy stuff that’s happening at Fairific HQ and the different views in the world of ethical trade. We use it to trends and share news, deals, contests, events, new features, cool stuff, and basically everything else that we’re up to. Dialogues is a bullhorn for the internet… except more polite and less awful. By weighing in on issues you care about or starting your own conversation, you make your voice heard. With the design scrapbook, you have free reign over product innovation and tons of helpful people to give you feedback. The gallery displays the best Fairific photos and videos created by the Fairific Community, so you can see how other folks are putting their Fairific goods to use. The Rewards Program is a two-part perks fest that helps you support causes you believe in while you ride the gravy train to great rewards. Finally, Events keeps you up to date on the comings and goings of us Fairifically busy bees. When we’re not buzzing around HQ making sweet, sweet ethical honey, we’re out hosting or throwing events so we can meet you, the good people of the world! While you’re moving and shaking between events, use the Fairific mobile app to stay connected to the whole shebang. The Fairific mobile app brings the Voting System to your smart phone, allowing you to spice up your long hauls by casting your vote for your favorite stuff. The app also lets you comment on products, post to Facebook, and even add items to your shopping cart. All the votes you cast using the app are automatically added to your voting record, accessible via your account on Fairific.com. And for those fleeting moments when you’re not online, Fairific is there for you at participating retailers right in your neighborhood. The in-store selling system fills the gap between the fun of homegrown stores and the breadth of big boxes by getting you access to the inventories of tons of ethical trade shops around the country when you visit a participating brick-and-mortar store in your city. Bottom line, you shop a selection like the big guys’ while supporting the local, ethical businesses you love.
Using the Fairific apps and features, you are changing the way things are made, bought, and sold, and at the end of the day you’re the one who makes it Fairific for all!
